<br>
In the meantime the cleric named Zyra didn't even attempt to heal Rasheeke in any way shape or form. That nasty DE watched him fall and offered no assistance. About this time a female Lightout came strutting by. They must have known each other. <br>
<br>
I told Zyra &quot;how about a rez for Rasheeke?&quot;  <br>
she replied &quot;no&quot;. <br>
<br>
I repeat. <br>
<br>
She says &quot;I have to go.&quot; She then runs off with this female Lightout. <br>
<br>
I said &quot;you can't rez?&quot; <br>
<br>
She says &quot;I can't rez&quot; <br>
<br>
When I conned her before she got into the group she was yellow. Ok She's about 2 levls higher than me, no biggie. Now she cons red. <br>
<br>
I asked her &quot;What level are you?&quot; <br>
<br>
She says &quot; I'm 12&quot;<br>
<br>
I said &quot;no, not your age, quit lying to me, you con red to me...&quot; <br>
<br>
She said &quot;I don't have time to rez.&quot; <br>
<br>
I said &quot;I see. You will never group with me again.&quot; <br>
<br>
She never replied back.<br>
<br>
It's not the idea that we couldn't get the exp back at such a low level within a few kills, it was the idea that she didn't want to help and I should have realized that and kicked her out to begin with. I will not go out of my way for her... ever.<br>
<br>
